{"tid":1144201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名宿：曼聯仍然極具吸引力 熱刺還比不上他們","createTime":"2019-05-08T03:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T05:08:45.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f89c9683e00748a65c18eab2bbf56191a70609f","tid":1144201,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"曼聯今季的狀態非常糟糕，這也讓外界擔心他們對優秀球員的吸引力是否會因此下降。曾同時效力過曼聯和熱刺的貝碧托夫表示，如果現在讓他選擇，他還是會選曼聯而不是熱刺。<br />\n<br />\n  「這裡仍然是曼聯，他們仍然擁有自己的標誌、歷史、過去的偉大球員、奧脫福，還有吸引力。好吧，你可能會說&lsquo;等等，熱刺在踢歐冠盃，他們有新球場，有很棒的訓練場，還有更好的球員&rsquo;，但最終我還是會選擇曼聯。」<br />\n<br />\n  貝碧托夫還開玩笑道：「他們現在都需要叫我回去！但是曼聯會很好。他們現在的狀態是不太好，但五年後他們能贏得獎盃嗎？答案是能，這也是我為什麼當初簽約了曼聯，為什麼即使到了今天我還是遵循於我的這種直覺。」<br />\n<br />\n  在談到普捷天奴時，貝碧托夫表示：「有時候你需要走出你的舒適區，即使你害怕結果。你需要這樣做來考驗自己，而普捷天奴有可能成為曼聯的主教練。」"},{"pid":"51586e286b063af6173f34384bad162c3e74888d","tid":1144201,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:07:07.000Z","msg":"緊係啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagesvc.timeincapp.com/v3/fan/image?url=https://fansided.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/229/files/2018/08/Premier-League-2018-19-average-player-salaries-by-club.jpg&amp;c=sc&amp;w=1943&amp;h=1516\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagesvc.timeincapp.com%2Fv3%2Ffan%2Fimage%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ffansided.com%2Fwp-content%2Fblogs.dir%2F229%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F08%2FPremier-League-2018-19-average-player-salaries-by-club.jpg%26c%3Dsc%26w%3D1943%26h%3D1516&h=0f744b72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac90a9a8afdd656babd008a4e9bd4ee185919f4","tid":1144201,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"魚拉突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0ce6f3c36d0b8bd6348578b71ab8391a121ce7","tid":1144201,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"想打拳應該去曼定熱好"},{"pid":"7d1f8540f2585e9932d03e03871b6bb6193c1c10","tid":1144201,"uid":88123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:22:43.000Z","msg":"前四都無搵邊個踢"},{"pid":"eeafcc973fe2de742354e83ed838a4e615a3e1ba","tid":1144201,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"今日無哂獌迷既"}]}